\f38\fs24\lang3081\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp3081\langfenp1033 {\insrsid8257942 identifying all the main goals and principles as early as possible, and leaving the details till the main structure is worked out;
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s40 \f38\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af38\dbch\af0\hich\f38 \'97\tab}reducing the number and complexity of the concepts in the scheme;
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s40 \f38\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af38\dbch\af0\hich\f38 \'97\tab}constructing the scheme clearly, using diagrams and flow-charts if necessary, before beginning to express it in legislative form.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s23 \f3\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}}\pard\plain \s23\ql \fi-720\li1440\ri0\sb240\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx1440\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls2\ilvl2\adjustright\rin0\lin1440\itap0 
\f38\fs24\lang3081\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp3081\langfenp1033 {\insrsid8257942 Second, to use the well-known rules of simple writing.  These include:
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s40 \f38\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af38\dbch\af0\hich\f38 \'97\tab}}\pard\plain \s40\ql \fi-621\li1701\ri0\sb240\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx1701\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls2\ilvl3\adjustright\rin0\lin1701\itap0 
\f38\fs24\lang3081\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp3081\langfenp1033 {\insrsid8257942 using short, well constructed sentences;
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s40 \f38\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af38\dbch\af0\hich\f38 \'97\tab}avoiding jargon and unfamiliar words;
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s40 \f38\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af38\dbch\af0\hich\f38 \'97\tab}using short words;
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s40 \f38\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af38\dbch\af0\hich\f38 \'97\tab}avoiding double and triple negatives;
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s40 \f38\lang3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8257942 \loch\af38\dbch\af0\hich\f38 \'97\tab}using the positive rather than the negative;
