\tx720\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls1\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11412465 \f38\fs24\lang3081\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp3081\langfenp1033 {\expnd0\expndtw-3\insrsid8257942 
Plain language drafting should be the fundamental style in all laws.  It can make laws very much}{\insrsid8257942  easier to understand.  Done in the proper way, it can maintain the high standards of precision aimed at by the traditional style.
